---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const seo = { title: 'Terms of Service — BrandsBuilders', description: 'Terms governing services provided by BrandsBuilders.', canonical: 'https://brandsbuilders.ca/terms-of-service' };
---
<Layout seo={seo}>
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: 2026-06-18</p>
    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
      <p>BrandsBuilders provides a website build, ad campaign management, creative testing, and missed-call recovery system, delivered as a single monthly service ("Tier 1").</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Services</h2>
      <p>Services include: a high-conversion website build or rebuild; management of Google Ads or Meta Ads on one platform; basic creative testing (2–3 ad variations per month); a dedicated tracked phone number; missed-call SMS protection; and monthly performance reporting.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Fees</h2>
      <p>$1,500/month flat service fee, billed month-to-month. Ad spend is separate and billed directly to the client's own ad account; a minimum of $500–$1,500/month is recommended for effective testing and results.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Reporting &amp; Transparency</h2>
      <p>Clients receive monthly reporting covering leads generated, cost per lead, lead source, and conversions. No fixed lead-volume guarantee is made; results depend on market, offer, and ad spend, and typically take time to optimize.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Ownership</h2>
      <p>The client retains ownership of their domain, ad accounts, and campaign data at all times.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the Province of Alberta and Canadian federal law.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Contact</h2>
      <p>BrandsBuilders · Alberta, Canada · <a href="mailto:hello@brandsbuilders.ca" class="text-orange-600">hello@brandsbuilders.ca</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
